i would like a recipe for a chocolate bundt cake made from scratch danke ingredients cups butter softened cups sugar eggs tsp vanilla cups buttermilk cups flour cup cocoa tsp baking powder tsp baking soda tsp salt cup peanut butter cups semisweet chocolate chips preparation preheat oven to degrees f spray a inch bundt pan with nonstick baking spray with flour in the spray and set aside in a large bowl beat butter and sugar until fluffy add eggs one at a time beating well after each addition beat in vanilla sift together flour cocoa baking powder baking soda and salt add alternately with buttermilk to butter mixture beginning and ending with dry ingredients pour batter into prepared pan bake at degrees f for minutes until toothpick inserted in cake comes out clean and cake begins to pull away from sides of pan cool in pan for minutes then turn onto serving plate and cool completely to frost melt peanut butter and semisweet chocolate chips in microwave minutes on power and stir until smooth spoon over cake servings hope you enjoy it it's great very moist and rich Pancake Japanese cuisine Cocoa Cookware and bakeware Jewish cuisine Ice cream Dim sum Dairy Cold Stone Creamery Dosa Baked Alaska Peanut butter Coffee Bacon Bagel Flour Rice pudding Cuisine of the Southern United States Kraft Dinner Milkshake Baking powder Tofu Cooking weights and measures Pizza Tea Vinegar Cuisine of the Philippines Baking Chili con carne Chocolate Salty Balls Wok Soul food Biscuit Cuisine of Denmark Muffin Halva Plastic Sandwich Butter French fries Cuisine of Brazil Ramen Souffl__ Brewery Twix Curry Haggis Cheesecake Soy protein Casting Maple syrup Barbecue German cuisine Puff pastry French toast Dumpling Hot dog Sugar Hot chocolate Recipe Mooncake Sushi D__ner kebab Cuisine of Singapore Bengali cuisine Rice Krispies Potato pancakes Gumbo Pottery Kit Kat Glass Peanut Risotto Peruvian cuisine Potato In-N-Out Burger Cooking Baklava Cuisine of Malaysia Korean cuisine Toffee Dairy product Micro